Package: FieldSimR
Title: Simulation of Plot Errors and Phenotypes in Plant Breeding Field Trials
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2023-02-02
Authors@R: c(person("Christian", "Werner", email = "werner.christian@proton.me", 
